This article showcases news, blog posts, and updates that VRChat published between January 1, 2022 and December 31, 2022.
==History==

Since 2016, VRChat's developer updates have been posted on several outlets, and have also gone through different names. Former developer updates have been called ''Developer Blogs'', ''Community Updates'', and ''Town Hall Meetings''.

From this year, VRChat migrated<ref>[https://hello.vrchat.com/blog/vrchat-blog-migration "VRChat Blog Migration"] on ''[https://hello.vrchat.com/blog VRChat's Blog]''. Dated January 20, 2022. Retrieved March 1, 2025.</ref> their blog, from [https://medium.com/vrchat Medium] to a [https://hello.vrchat.com/blog self-hosted blog]. Starting in July 2022, VRChat began posting Developer Updates regularly, twice per week, on the Ask Forums.

